<h2> Chapter One Setting</h2></br></br></br>
<div id="sand">
Desert: Sand</br></br></br></br></br></br></br></br>
</div>
<div id="arena">
Setting: The walls widen out to form a large circle(arena).</br></br></br>
The sand is blown down from the right slope. It is piled up in the ____ side of the circle.</br></br></br>
The right wall slopes out steeply(about 75 degrees out of circle), with holes(windows) in the side.</br></br></br>
As the wall goes around the circle, it slopes into the circle (about 80 degrees) on the left.</br></br></br></br>
</div>

